Gist

To download and execute gist, run the commands below:

#!/bin/bash

# wget https://github.com/thehardeningproject/GIST/archive/master.zip
# unzip GIST-master.zip
# cd GIST-master/
# chmod +x install.sh
# ./install.sh


Required Programs

The installation program will download this dependencies:

	Nmap
	Dnsutils/bind-utils
	Python36
	Whois


